{"tid":912554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大師入市】麥玲玲1748萬入市寶馬山花園","createTime":"2018-11-22T18:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T08:23:55.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e5af0433a2d70317e92a2742fc3eb71601faa021","tid":912554,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T18:16:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20181121/s00011/1723a2e395e31ee50275f47b435441a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20181121%2Fs00011%2F1723a2e395e31ee50275f47b435441a6.jpg&h=129372a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然樓市調整，不少買家都抱觀望態度，不過市場消息指，玄學家麥玲玲或有關人士新近以約1748萬元購入北角寶馬山花園一個6座中高層單位，實用面積845方呎，較業主原叫價2000萬元大減252萬元或12.6%，實呎20686元，計劃作投資用途。<br />\n<br />\n原業主2007年以718萬元購入，持貨11年現帳面獲利1030萬元，賺幅約1.4倍。"},{"pid":"458855856418b00c2899182b5d88568287f70513","tid":912554,"uid":110988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T22:17:41.000Z","msg":"唔知大師請唔請男秘書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79496105b8c71f83cb046cc6f7278d6b2611191f","tid":912554,"uid":46245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T23:51:42.000Z","msg":"好似瘦左？"},{"pid":"dbb49f629381e78ea5b354e00aaab74d27fe31c3","tid":912554,"uid":50457,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T00:22:43.000Z","msg":"我一出世就識睇梅花易數<br />\n用咗廿年羅庚東南西北梗係分到<br />\n我掌又睇到 相又睇到<br />\n要Rap都完全冇難度<br />\n鼻頭好有肉 內心就冇毒<br />\n眼睛水汪汪 桃花運暢旺<br />\n眉尾散 儲錢難<br />\n上唇厚重情 下唇厚比較重性"},{"pid":"4b6fe63b4740965f161713a8ce9f805437eace41","tid":912554,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T00:35:00.000Z","msg":"宗教係最呃錢"},{"pid":"84d91228aa1fc5f24eb256e520cd0b4ae16d20e4","tid":912554,"uid":223256,"like":1,"dislike":2,"s